VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT ^[^*/]*(setuid|setgid|initgroups)\s*\(\s*[^)]+\s*\)\s*[^/]*$
WHEN EXPR MISSING:if\s*\(|==\s*-1|!=\s*0|perror|strerror|errno
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects the usage of privilege management functions that need proper ordering for secure operation.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Improper Privilege Dropping.
